title: RCL Crosses Above Key Moving Average Level - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Wednesday, shares of Royal Caribbean Cruises Ltd (Symbol: RCL) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $114.09, changing hands as high as $114.38 per share. Royal Caribbean Cruises Ltd shares are currently trading down about 0.2% on the day. The chart below shows the one year performance of RCL shares, versus its 200 day moving average:     Looking at the chart above, RCL's low point in its 52 week range is $89.48 per share, with $133.60 as the 52 week high point - that compares with a last trade of $113.53.
